com.google.enterprise.connector.sharepoint.wsclient
Class GSBulkAuthorizationWS

java.lang.Object
  com.google.enterprise.connector.sharepoint.wsclient.GSBulkAuthorizationWS

public class GSBulkAuthorizationWS
extends java.lang.Object

Java Client for calling GSBulkAuthorization.asmx. Provides a layer to talk to the GSBulkAuthorization Web Service deployed on the SharePoint server. Any call to this Web Service must go through this layer.

Author:
nitendra_thakur
